full_content:
Function: acl_delete_entry
URL: https://www.qnx.com/developers/docs/7.1/com.qnx.doc.neutrino.lib_ref/topic/a/acl_delete_entry.html
Synopsis: int acl_delete_entry( acl_t acl,
Headers: #include <sys/acl.h>
Parameters:
  - acl: A pointer to the ACL that you want to delete an entry from.
  - entry_d: The descriptor of the entry that you want to delete.
Examples:
Example 1:
#include <sys/acl.h>

int acl_delete_entry( acl_t acl,
                      acl_entry_t entry_d );
